Required icon files:
  icon.png       — 512×512 app icon (Linux + fallback)
  icon.ico       — Windows multi-resolution icon
  icon.icns      — macOS icon bundle
  tray-idle.png  — 16×16 grayscale tray icon (no active jobs)
  tray-active.png — 16×16 colour tray icon (job printing)

Generate with: https://www.icoconverter.com/ (ICO) and iconutil (ICNS)
